# AGENTS.md — {{ .AppName }}

## MCP Server

Apus runs at `http://localhost:{{ .MCPPort }}/mcp` when the app is running in the simulator or on a device.

## Build & Run

```bash
PROJECT_ROOT="$(pwd)"
DERIVED_DATA="$PROJECT_ROOT/.build/DerivedData"

# Boot simulator (idempotent)
xcrun simctl boot {{ .SimulatorUDID }} >/dev/null 2>&1 || true

# Build
xcodebuild -project {{ .AppName }}.xcodeproj \
  -scheme {{ .AppName }} \
  -destination "id={{ .SimulatorUDID }}" \
  -derivedDataPath "$DERIVED_DATA" \
  -quiet CODE_SIGN_IDENTITY="-"

# Install freshly built app bundle
xcrun simctl install {{ .SimulatorUDID }} "$DERIVED_DATA/Build/Products/Debug-iphonesimulator/{{ .AppName }}.app"

# Launch (force restart + pass project root to app process)
SIMCTL_CHILD_APUS_PROJECT_ROOT="$PROJECT_ROOT" \
  xcrun simctl launch --terminate-running-process {{ .SimulatorUDID }} com.{{ .BundleOrg }}.{{ .AppNameLower }}

# If simctl rejects --terminate-running-process, retry without that flag.
SIMCTL_CHILD_APUS_PROJECT_ROOT="$PROJECT_ROOT" \
  xcrun simctl launch {{ .SimulatorUDID }} com.{{ .BundleOrg }}.{{ .AppNameLower }}
```

## Key MCP Tools

| Tool | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `get_logs` | App console output |
| `get_screenshot` | Current screen as JPEG |
| `get_view_hierarchy` | Full SwiftUI/UIKit view tree |
| `ui_interact` | tap, double_tap, swipe, type_text |
| `get_network_history` | All HTTP/HTTPS traffic |
| `hot_reload` | Inject Swift changes without recompile |
| `get_memory_usage` | Live memory stats |

## Quick Start

```
POST http://localhost:{{ .MCPPort }}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"get_screenshot","arguments":{}}}
```
